<div class="flex flex-col justify-center sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
  <div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-3xl">
    <h2 class="mt-6 text-center text-3xl leading-9 font-extrabold text-gray-900">
      Our Story
    </h2>
     <p class="mt-8 text-center text-sm leading-5 text-gray-600 max-w">
      Over 210,000 dead. 8% unemployed. Temperatures rising. Wildfires. Smoke-filled air. 
      George Floyd. Breonna Taylor. Jacob Blake. Say their names. 
      On the zipcode level, 23,000+ cases in <%= CITY_NAME %> county alone. 445 deaths. 
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4 text-center text-sm leading-5 text-gray-600 max-w">
      We are living in a nation divided. But in the midst of a global pandemic and climate related risk, 
      it’s small businesses, people of color, the elderly, the environment, and low-income communities 
      who are disproportionately impacted.  
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4 text-center text-sm leading-5 text-gray-600 max-w">
      The data looks grim. But on a local level, we can make a difference. 
      When communities come together, we can make it work. 
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4 text-center text-sm leading-5 text-gray-600 max-w">
      ResiTown is brought to you by Community Connections: Sacramento. In partnership with the Clinton Foundation, 
      City Help with COVID, and CSU Northridge's Innovation Corps, we are dedicated to bringing people together and 
      activating positive change. 
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4 text-center text-sm leading-5 text-gray-600 max-w">
      We believe that engaged and connected communities are not only healthier, but also more equitable and resilient. In the 
      face of COVID-19, we want to help local economies thrive—by connecting students, retirees, individuals looking for work, 
      and professionals with meaningful opportunities. 
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4 mb-4 text-center text-sm leading-5 text-gray-600 max-w">
      Welcome to our community. We're happy to have you. 
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-3xl">
    <a id='how-it-works'>
      <h2 class="mt-6 text-center text-3xl leading-9 font-extrabold text-gray-900">
        How Does It Work?
      </h2>
    </a>
     <p class="mt-8 text-center text-sm leading-5 text-gray-600 max-w">
      ResiTown is a web-based platform, where you’ll be able to sign-up for local opportunities - both in-person and remote. 
    </p>
    <h3 class="mt-6 text-center text-2xl leading-9 font-extrabold text-gray-900">
    Here are step-by-step instructions:
    </h3>
    <div class="flex justify-center">
    <p class="mt-8 text-center text-sm leading-5 text-gray-600 max-w">
      <ol id="instructions" class="mt-4 list-none pl-15 text-sm leading-5 text-gray-600">
        <li>1. Create a profile on the ResiTown website or click here</li>
        <li>2. Find a volunteer opportunity that you're interested in</li>
        <li>3. Sign-up for the opportunity</li>
        <li>4. Sit tight and an email with additional details will be sent to your inbox</li>
      </ol>  
    </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="flex flex-col mt-8">
    <div class="-my-2 py-2 overflow-x-auto sm:-mx-6 sm:px-6 lg:-mx-8 lg:px-8">
      <div class="align-middle inline-block min-w-full shadow overflow-hidden sm:rounded-lg border-b border-gray-200">
        <table id="team-table" class="min-w-full">
          <tbody>
          <% striped_classes_cycle = [ "bg-white", "bg-gray-50" ] %>
          <% TEAM.each do |group, team| %>
            <% if !group.empty? %>
              <tr class="<%= cycle striped_classes_cycle %>">
                <td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-no-wrap text-sm leading-5 font-medium text-white text-center bg-primary-500">
                  <%= html_escape group %>
                </td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-no-wrap text-sm leading-5 text-gray-500 text-center bg-primary-500">
                </td>
              </tr>
            <% end %>
            <% team.each do |name, role| %>
              <tr class="<%= cycle striped_classes_cycle %>">
                <td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-no-wrap text-sm leading-5 font-medium text-gray-900 text-center">
                  <%= html_escape name %>
                </td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-no-wrap text-sm leading-5 text-gray-500 text-center">
                  <%= html_escape role %>
                </td>
              </tr>
            <% end %>
          <% end %>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="sm:mx-auto sm:w-full sm:max-w-lg">
    <h2 class="mt-8 text-center text-3xl leading-9 font-extrabold text-gray-900">
      Thank you to all volunteers!
    </h2>
  </div>
</div>
